{SCRIPT: Initiate combat. PC starts at some kind of disadvantage. Low initiative?}</FemaleText>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>80</ID>
      <DefaultText>He breathes a sigh of relief. "Thank you, lad. I owe you one."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>81</ID>
      <DefaultText>""</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>82</ID>
      <DefaultText>Script Node 82</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>83</ID>
      <DefaultText>"This isn't over, you self-serving bastard." Ris jabs a finger in Tybir's face. "Hide behind your friend if you like, but he won't keep you safe forever."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText>"This isn't over, you self-serving bastard." Ris jabs a finger in Tybir's face. "Hide behind your friend if you like, but she won't keep you safe forever."</FemaleText>
    </Entry>
